Construction Engineer
Location:  --Abu Dhabi
Abu Dhabi has currently one of the strongest Oil driven economies in the world. Want to become a part of it? Want to secure a stable future for you and your family? Abu Dhabi can help you do this.My client is a leading Operating Company who is looking to grow on an international scale. They are looking to recruit Construction Engineer.
The candidate should have an Offshore experience within the Oil and Gas industry.
The requirements are as follows:
B.Sc. or equivalnet degree in Engineering
MUST have Offshore experience
MUST have Operator background (ex: EXXON, RasGas, TOTAL, Marsek, Shell, etc)
Experience in Fabrication will be an advantage.
MUST have 10 years’ experience in the Oil and Gas industry (offshore/onshore) with extensive hands-on experience in Construction Engineering.
Please note that only candidates who are meeting the requirements will be shortlisted for the next stage.
